Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:17.24,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}I'm tossed into the fray
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:19.07,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}tossed by various fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:20.76,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}wake up your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:22.77,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}flashed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:25.32,lrc_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an8}It's a burst of sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:31.62,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「諦め」がくれた安楽  沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:34.55,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつからだっただろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:37.81,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:41.06,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変わらずにいてと願うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.67,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変わりゆく時に生きる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:46.32,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の声を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:47.90,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}言い得ぬ夢を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:50.32,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君と繋がった空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:52.12,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}響かせて！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.09,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もっと強く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:59.42,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:02.81,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「今度こそは…」つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:06.02,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷さえも無駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:09.38,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:12.56,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:15.98,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歪む世界走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:19.10,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}感覚のその向うへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.19,0:23:24.66,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「真実」と 加速してく
